      "overview_item_data": {
        "overview_item_data_type": "list",
        "overview_item_data_items": [
          "A simulation is an experiment that models a real-life situation.",
          "When conducting a simulation, you must choose a model that has the same probability as the event.",
          "As the number of trials in an experiment increases, the experimental probability approaches the theoretical probability.",
          "You can use technology to generate random numbers to perform a simulation."
